# Deployment Identification

Our applications follow Blue-Green deployment.

Example deployments:

order-management-ms-blue

order-management-ms-green

Only one deployment should be active.

Determine the active deployment using Pod availability.

Rules:

If only one deployment has running pods

→ Active Deployment

If both deployments have running pods

→ Treat as inconsistent deployment

→ Ignore deployment

→ Log warning

→ Continue processing remaining deployments

